Factory Assistant OS landing page

Factory Assistant is based on Home Assistant.

The landingpage image reuses the upstream-compatible Home Assistant OS
landingpage server binary as the HTTP, redirect, proxy, and mDNS runtime.
The visible static web root in /usr/share/www is Factory Assistant content.

